cdata.name: B2BX
cdata.desc:
B2BXis a cryptocurrency liquidity aggregator formarginand exchange trading while also providing distribution of liquidity to broker companies. B2BX will focus exclusively on institutional clients: crypto exchange, brokers, FOREX brokers, DMA brokers, cryptocurrency brokers, hedge funds and other professional market participants.

The product is ready and it is in its alpha stage. B2BX will useSoftFX aggregatoras a basic solution since it is already integrated with the 5 major crypto-exchanges and the project already has 12 institutional clients for this product. The project uses the FIX API protocol for further distribution of liquidity to other systems and aggregators.
